message:
[cli] Add --device to asteroid-infer (#375)

Defaults to CUDA if available

Co-authored-by: Manuel Pariente <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>

[src] Fix #279 OLA support for separate() and asteroid-infer (#305)

Co-authored-by: Pariente Manuel <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>
[src] BC-breaking: Load models without sample_rate (#285)
[src&tests] Automatic resampling in separate + CLI. (#283)
[black] Update black to 20.8b1 (#265)
[CLI] Refactor `separate` method (future torch.script compat) (#245)
[CLI] Add asteroid-infer CLI to enhance/separate from the command line (#236)
[black] Flake8 compatibility + Black strings (#198)
[black] Change formatting with black using default config and line-length 100 (#197)
[docs] Brand new docs ! (#192)
[model_cards] Add message to create model card after publishing
[src & egs] Publishing pretrained models !! (wham/ConvTasNet) (#125)

[install] Upgrade dependencies to torch 2.x and lightning 2.x (#682)

* Update Lighting and Torch requirements to 2.X

* Remove optimizer_idx from `lr_scheduler_step` in System

* Replace torch.symeig with torch.linalg.eigh in beamforming

* Disable X_UMX model in torch2.x (complex STFT needs to be used)

* Skip XUMX tests until it is fixed.

* Replace on_x_end to on_train_x_end

* Replace torch.testing.assert_allclose with torch.testing.assert_close.

* Black it
[src&tests] Remove deprecated code (#474)

[src] Add mulcat option to DPRNN (#416)

Co-authored-by: Joseph Zhu <junzhez2@ifp-10.ifp.uiuc.edu>
Co-authored-by: Pariente Manuel <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>

[src&egs] Add FasNetTAC model, dataset and recipe  (#306)

* TAC masker network
* FasNetTAC model
* TAC recipe with TACDataset and FasNetTAC model
* Add asteroid.dsp.xcorr

Co-authored-by: Pariente Manuel <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: Iver Jordal <1470603+iver56@users.noreply.github.com>
[src] Change n_channels to in_channels (#432)
[src] Fix unpassed SR in TasNet and SudoRMRF (#433)
[src] Make sample_rate positional in BaseModel (#431)

[src] Support Multichannel models (#427)

* Add n_channels to BaseModel

* Load/save test for multichannel models

* Add n_channels to Separatable

* Multichannel in separate

* Add n_channels to LambdaOverlapAdd

[src] Add stft_n_filters to BaseDCUNet (#406)

Backward breaking: change default parameter to match DCUNet paper

[src] Fix Large-DCUNet-20 arch (#405)

And add tests for the bigger architectures

Co-authored-by: Manuel Pariente <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>

[hub] Support for huggingface model hub :tada: (#377)

Co-authored-by: Pariente Manuel <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>

[src&tests] Fix complex and add tests (#358)

- Add CLI tests
- Add tests for complex_nn
- Deprecate `as_torch_complex`
- Fix DCCRN
[CI] Catch warnings we expect (#351)

[src&jit] Fix DCCRN and DCUNet-Large (#276)

- Fix the architectures
- JIT-able DCCRN and DCUNet
- Automatic reshaping in DCUNet 

Co-authored-by: Pariente Manuel <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>

[src] BaseModel takes sample_rate argument (#336)

Addresses #318 by adding an optional sample_rate argument to BaseModel with a property getter and setter.
[src] New asteroid.show_available_models (#313)

[src & tests] :tada: TorchScript support :tada: (#237)

Jitability of most Asteroid features (filterbanks, encoder/decoder, norms, activations, masker, architecture, utils etc..) with tracing + automatic scripting when tracing on necessary modules. 
Extended type-hints to several places.
Backward-breaking changes: `filters` property not a property anymore (call `filters()` instead)

Co-authored-by: popcornell <cornellsamuele@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: mpariente <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: HU Mathieu <mathieu.hu@inria.fr>
Co-authored-by: mhu-coder <mathieu.hu12@gmail.com>

Co-authored-by: mpariente <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>
[tests] Fix models_test.py

[src & egs] Add DeMask: Surgical mask speech enhancement recipes (#235)

Co-authored-by: mpariente <pariente.mnl@gmail.com>
[tests] Fix wrong `separate` method in model tests (#241)
[tests] Improve tests for new model interface (#234)
Merge branch 'master' into tasnet

[src & tests] Fix serialization issues introduced in previous PR + some docs (#204)

[src & tests] Add SuDoRM-RF model & online mixing collate function (#174)
